com.premiumminds.webapp.wicket

Class AndMessageFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.premiumminds.webapp.wicket.AndMessageFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.apache.wicket.feedback.IFeedbackMessageFilter, org.apache.wicket.util.io.IClusterable

    public class AndMessageFilter
extends Object
implements org.apache.wicket.feedback.IFeedbackMessageFilter
    Filter that matches only messages that are matched by ALL added filters (thus implementing a logical AND operation). Allows for flexible composition of existing filters. Example use (filters provided in constructor): IFeedbackMessageFilter filter = new CompositeAndMessageFilter( new ComponentFeedbackMessageFilter(ResetPasswordPanel.this), new ExactErrorLevelFilter(FeedbackMessage.ERROR) ); Example use (with chaining): IFeedbackMessageFilter filter = new CompositeAndMessageFilter() .add(new ComponentFeedbackMessageFilter(ResetPasswordPanel.this)) .add(new ExactErrorLevelFilter(FeedbackMessage.ERROR));
